<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c3">{إِن بَطش رَبك}</span> عُقُوبَة رَبك <span class="c3">{لشديد}</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ مُحَمَّدٌ:</span> <span class="c2">(إِنَّ بَطْشَ رَبِّكَ لشديد)</span> هُوَ جَوَابُ الْقَسَمِ <span class="c2">(وَالسَّمَاءِ ذَاتِ الْبُرُوجِ)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>